<ul>
<li><strong>Karina Häuslmeier</strong>, Deputy Head of Mission, German Embassy Ottawa</li>
<li><strong>Astrid Shomaker</strong>, Director for Green Diplomacy and Multilateralism, Directorate General for Environment, European Commission</li>
<p>&nbsp;
</ul>
<h4 class="presenting-speakers">Featuring</h3>
<ul>
