<li><strong>Stephen Leahy</strong>, International Environmental Journalist</li>
<li><strong>Christian Schwägerl</strong>, Environment and Science Journalist, Managing Director Riff Free Media, Berlin</li>
<li>Moderated by <strong>Saroja Coelho</strong>, Host, CBC Music and CBC Radio One</li>
</ul>
